<h2>Introduction for <a href="http://ph7cms.com">pH7 Social Dating CMS</a></h2>

<p>
    <strong>pH7CMS</strong> is a CMS to build an online dating service or social network website. It is written in object-oriented PHP (OOP) with a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Model%E2%80%93view%E2%80%93controller">MVC</a> pattern (Model-View-Controller).<br />
    It is designed with the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/KISS_principle">KISS principle</a> in mind, and the all source code can be read and understood in minutes. For the best flexibility, pH7CMS also uses <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PHP_Data_Objects">PDO</a> (PHP Data Objects) abstraction which allows the choice of the database.<br />
    The principle of development is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_repeat_yourself">DRY</a> (Don't Repeat Yourself) aimed at reducing repetition of information of all kinds (not duplicate code).</p>

<p>It also wants to be fast, low-resource-intensive, extremely powerful and very secure.</p>
<p>In addition to being <strong>free</strong>, <strong>open source</strong> and <strong>relatively stable</strong>, the software comes with more than <strong>35 native modules</strong> and based on <strong>pH7Framework</strong> which includes over 50 packages.</p>
